	<description>	
		
		Stickin' the landing is a puzzle game where the player has to help navigate a spaceship adrift with gravitational forces until it reaches the finish line.
		Travel your house with the help of different stickers and avoid the obstacles you encounter in the adventure exploring the galaxy of your imagination.

		Put stickers and manage the gravitational force to arrive at your destination.
	</description>
		
	<histories>
		
		<history>
			<header>Early prototipe (2021)</header>
			<text>We are a group of college classmates who took advantage of the existence of a non-profit company at the university to develop and publish video games. The last year of university we finally created our own team.
				Originally Chema, Marko and Javier with the help of another student outside of the actual project, Victor, had to create a game for a group assignment. The game was made with the goal of passing the subject but we recognized that it had potential.</text>
		</history>
		<history>
			<header>Current Development (2023)</header>
			<text>Two years after the first prototype we decided to revisit the idea for the Videogame Production subject and make a full game. We passed the subject and went on to produce the game. Since we needed some help with some parts of the game we decided to add new members until we were a team composed by 10 members.</text>
		</history>
	</histories>
		
